Fix the left panel (.auth-left) styling in Auth.css only. 
Do not touch any TSX logic.

1. LAYOUT — vertically distribute content:
   .auth-left {
     display: flex;
     flex-direction: column;
     justify-content: space-between;
     padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
   }

2. HEADLINE — fix font and size:
   .auth-left h2, .auth-left .auth-headline {
     font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
     font-size: 2.2rem;
     font-weight: 800;
     line-height: 1.2;
     color: #ffffff;
     letter-spacing: -0.02em;
   }

3. SUBTEXT:
   .auth-left .auth-subtext {
     font-size: 0.92rem;
     color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
     line-height: 1.6;
     margin-top: 0.75rem;
     max-width: 340px;
   }

4. FEATURE PILLS — make them cleaner:
   .feature-item {
     background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
     border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
     backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
     border-radius: 999px;
     padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem;
     font-size: 0.84rem;
     font-weight: 500;
     color: #ffffff;
     display: inline-flex;
     align-items: center;
     gap: 0.5rem;
     width: fit-content;
   }
   .feature-list {
     margin-top: 2rem;
     display: flex;
     flex-direction: column;
     gap: 0.65rem;
   }

5. ADD a mock visual card at the bottom of .auth-left 
   to fill the empty space. Add a new div .mock-visual 
   in Login.tsx and Register.tsx inside .auth-left, 
   just above the copyright line:

   <div class="mock-visual">
     <div class="mock-bar"></div>
     <div class="mock-bar short"></div>
     <div class="mock-wave">
       <div class="wave-block"></div>
       <div class="wave-block tall"></div>
       <div class="wave-block medium"></div>
       <div class="wave-block tall"></div>
       <div class="wave-block short"></div>
       <div class="wave-block medium"></div>
       <div class="wave-block tall"></div>
       <div class="wave-block"></div>
     </div>
   </div>

   Style in Auth.css:
   .mock-visual {
     background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
     border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
     border-radius: 18px;
     padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
     margin-top: 2.5rem;
     backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
   }
   .mock-bar {
     height: 10px;
     background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
     border-radius: 999px;
     margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
     width: 70%;
   }
   .mock-bar.short { width: 45%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
   .mock-wave {
     display: flex;
     align-items: flex-end;
     gap: 5px;
     margin-top: 1rem;
     height: 48px;
   }
   .wave-block {
     flex: 1;
     background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
     border-radius: 4px;
     height: 40%;
   }
   .wave-block.tall  { height: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
   .wave-block.medium { height: 65%; }
   .wave-block.short { height: 25%; }

6. COPYRIGHT:
   .auth-left .auth-copyright {
     font-size: 0.72rem;
     color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
     margin-top: 1.5rem;
   }

